17
00:03:14,991 --> 00:03:16,515
Happy birthday.

18
00:03:20,263 --> 00:03:21,252
(BELLA CLICKS TONGUE)

19
00:03:21,397 --> 00:03:22,921
I thought we agreed, no presents.

20
00:03:22,999 --> 00:03:26,560
Well, the one from me's not wrapped,
so it doesn't count.

21
00:03:30,873 --> 00:03:33,034
That's actually great. Thanks, Dad.

22
00:03:33,442 --> 00:03:37,310
It goes with this one from your mom.
We coordinated.

23
00:03:37,580 --> 00:03:39,639
Well, she coordinated me.

24
00:03:41,517 --> 00:03:44,975
It's to put your pictures in
from senior year.

25
00:03:46,556 --> 00:03:48,683
(SIGHS) Senior year.

26
00:03:49,659 --> 00:03:53,288
- How'd you get so old so fast?
- I didn't. It's not that old.

27
00:03:53,596 --> 00:03:56,156
I don't know. Is that a gray hair?

28
00:03:56,832 --> 00:03:58,265
No. No way.

29
00:04:00,369 --> 00:04:01,358
(SIGHS)

30
00:04:02,405 --> 00:04:03,963
Happy birthday.

31
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:05,473
That's really funny.

32
